{{short description|Maldivian film actor and playback singer}} {{Infobox person | name = Abdullah Shafiu Ibrahim | image = | imagesize = | alt = Shafiu posing for camera wearing a blue jacket | caption = Ibrahim at ''[[Maamui]]'' premiere night, 2019 | birth_date = | birth_place = | alma_mater = | occupation = Actor, playback singer | yearsactive = 2016‚Äìpresent | spouse = | children = | works = | awards = }} '''Abdullah Shafiu Ibrahim''' is a Maldivian film actor and playback singer.
